{"tid":1927832,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解唔想大爆發？加速攬炒有咩唔好?","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T04:45:45.000Z","uid":341040,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8222707c05395af5ccdbde65197272ba2c426cb9","tid":1927832,"uid":341040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"加速攬炒有咩唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正香港爛到貼地 重新開機有咩唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎真係最強手足<br />\n<br />\n和你飛幾十個手足被拉，機場停得2日<br />\n<br />\n而家黎緊幾個月，日日機場都拍得鬼片</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">之前示威得旺角銅鑼灣停，上水d藥房繼續爆棚<br />\n<br />\n而家黎緊全香港都拍烏蠅，重新大洗牌</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">之前叔一燒燒得一條友，另加一條廢老比人掉死<br />\n<br />\n而家有機會死20萬廢老，死曬呢堆廢老就有機會立法會翻盤</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">示威幾個月都係冇popo死，<br />\n而家有機會用肺炎殺班popo</span><br />\n<br />\n快d攬炒唔好等"},{"pid":"20a741fd6c8625de042dc3d9f6bb27eab5cd9e9b","tid":1927832,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"【攻略】光復功能組別強化策略 (3月起啟用)<br />\n<br />\n✅全民 &gt; 組社團 + 組工會 + 開公司<br />\n✅專業人士 &gt; 登記專業界別<br />\n✅本身有BR &gt; 直接登記商界<br />\n✅手足 &gt; 掃黃店<br />\n<br />\n🔺組工會 (勞工界)<br />\n- 已確認核實，即使工會審批時間長短<br />\n- 只要你5月2日前提交申請, 就可以趕及2021特首選委🔥<br />\n組隊神器 7起 &gt; <a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=c2c4055d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a><br />\n無敵Q&amp;A &gt; <a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_12.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_12.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=ec49a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_12.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺開公司 (萬能界)<br />\n- 帶身份證去灣仔税局搞，俾$250，30分鐘搞掂 @businessfrontier<br />\n- 輕量級 &gt; 紡織界 $61/ 體育界 $2000/ 出版界 $1140 (撳個掣就得)<br />\n- 重量級 &gt; 商界 $3900/ 工業界 $2970/ 零售界 $1180/ 僱主聯合會 $4800<br />\n- 集中首選 &gt; 進出口界 $240+1320 (1年以上BR+商業地址）<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_57.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a286af00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺申請進出口牌 (進出口界）<br />\n只要有一年以上BR同埋商業地址，唔理你做咩生意，都可以向海關申請進出口牌，立即成為進出口界公司選民<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/exportfrontier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fexportfrontier&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=8796f25d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/exportfrontier</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexportfrontier%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=0cec1f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺掃黃店 (飲食界、零售界)<br />\n組隊幫手登記 &gt; <a href=\"https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fam8LThtTL9r6joL17&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=c6e4e28f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17</a><br />\n掃黃店進度表 &gt; <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cEJGz6&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=129d5789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6</a><br />\n黃店名單 &gt; <a href=\"https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkshoplist.com%2Fselect.php&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=8b09d949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺組社團 (文化界)<br />\n1. 齊集三人，須有相關文化資歷證明<br />\n2. 準備社團資料 - 宗旨/ 規章/ 擬辦活動<br />\n3. 準備個人資料 - 身分證副本/ 住址+會址證明 (3個月內)(銀行/水電煤單據)<br />\n4. 約組員出黎，互簽名，互交換文件<br />\n5. 寄出去 /親身交到警總 Done!<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_33.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a9eb6d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺每個香港人都可以拎三票<br />\n1. 地區個人票 (地方選區有得投）<br />\n2. 功能組別個人票 (正常人係超區)<br />\n3. 功能組別團體票(不可跟2同一界別)<br />\n<br />\n例子, 地方選區：香港島/ 功能界別(個人票)：超級區議會/ 功能界別(團體票)：飲食界<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_57.html%3Fm%3D1&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=94be063e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n重點功能界別的whatapps Hotline<br />\nGeneral whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n 體演文出whatapps Hotline : 66700860<br />\n 進出口界whatapps Hotline : 68461562<br />\n 飲食界whatapps Hotline : 9180 3949 / 66812202<br />\n 批發及零售whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n<br />\n📣 請訂閱作戰研究院 Telegram Channel ➼ @FightResearch<br />\n戰術研究 | 抗爭資訊 | 時局分析 | 評論 | 趣事<br />\nCredits to 七起"},{"pid":"734ab498ab4b57602d3d66a4245767dbfabc8692","tid":1927832,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabebf5f9df6030a5b1eeac2344bb35275adad6a","tid":1927832,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"